@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List all feedback
GET {{baseUrl}}/feedback

### Filter feedback by topic
GET {{baseUrl}}/feedback?topic=copilot-chat

### Filter feedback by minimum score
GET {{baseUrl}}/feedback?minScore=4

### Create feedback
POST {{baseUrl}}/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "Liam",
  "topic": "copilot-cli",
  "score": 5,
  "comment": "Very useful once I gave it a narrow task and a spec."
}

### Feedback summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/feedback/summary
